{"image_id": "PPL_2008_page_58", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "43", "bbox": [606.6, 1553.3, 632.3, 1575.9]}, {"text": "Dividends", "bbox": [47.1, 100.5, 135.2, 123.1]}, {"text": "PPL views dividend growth as an integral component of", "bbox": [47.1, 147.4, 511.9, 170.0]}, {"text": "shareowner return and expects to continue its trend of common", "bbox": [47.1, 170.9, 568.0, 193.6]}, {"text": "stock dividend increases.  In 2008, PPL increased the annualized", "bbox": [47.1, 194.3, 581.7, 217.0]}, {"text": "dividend rate on its common stock from $1.22 to $1.34 per", "bbox": [47.1, 217.9, 533.5, 240.5]}, {"text": "share, effective with the April 1, 2008 dividend payment.  In", "bbox": [47.1, 241.4, 547.7, 264.0]}, {"text": "2009, PPL increased the annualized dividend rate on its", "bbox": [47.1, 264.8, 507.0, 287.5]}, {"text": "common stock from $1.34 to $1.38 per share, effective with the", "bbox": [47.1, 288.3, 572.7, 311.0]}, {"text": "April 1, 2009 dividend payment.  Future dividends will be", "bbox": [47.1, 311.9, 527.9, 334.5]}, {"text": "declared at the discretion of the Board of Directors and will", "bbox": [47.1, 335.3, 539.0, 357.9]}, {"text": "depend upon available earnings, cash flows, financial", "bbox": [47.1, 358.8, 489.2, 381.5]}, {"text": "requirements and other relevant factors at the time.  As", "bbox": [47.1, 382.2, 501.7, 404.9]}, {"text": "discussed in Note 8 to the Financial Statements, PPL may not", "bbox": [47.1, 405.8, 555.4, 428.4]}, {"text": "declare or pay any cash dividend on its common stock during", "bbox": [47.1, 429.3, 554.0, 451.9]}, {"text": "any period in which PPL Capital Funding defers interest", "bbox": [47.1, 452.7, 513.3, 475.4]}, {"text": "payments on its 2007 Series A Junior Subordinated Notes due", "bbox": [47.1, 476.2, 558.9, 498.9]}, {"text": "2067.  No such deferrals have occurred or are currently", "bbox": [47.1, 499.8, 503.9, 522.4]}, {"text": "anticipated.", "bbox": [47.1, 523.2, 147.1, 545.8]}, {"text": "PPL Electric expects to continue to pay quarterly dividends on", "bbox": [47.1, 570.2, 563.6, 592.9]}, {"text": "its outstanding preferred securities, if and as declared by its", "bbox": [47.1, 593.7, 537.7, 616.3]}, {"text": "Board of Directors.", "bbox": [47.1, 617.2, 210.7, 639.8]}, {"text": "See Note 8 to the Financial Statements for other restrictions", "bbox": [47.1, 664.1, 540.8, 686.8]}, {"text": "related to distributions on capital interests for PPL subsidiaries.", "bbox": [47.1, 687.7, 570.3, 710.3]}, {"text": "Purchase of Debt Securities", "bbox": [47.1, 734.6, 281.0, 757.3]}, {"text": "On February 17, 2009, PPL Energy Supply initiated cash tender", "bbox": [47.1, 786.2, 574.8, 808.8]}, {"text": "offers for up to $250 million aggregate principal amount of", "bbox": [47.1, 809.6, 535.9, 832.2]}, {"text": "certain of its outstanding senior notes.  The series of notes, in", "bbox": [47.1, 833.1, 553.3, 855.8]}, {"text": "order of their priority level for acceptance by PPL Energy", "bbox": [47.1, 856.6, 524.7, 879.3]}, {"text": "Supply, are as follows:  6.00% Senior Notes due 2036, 6.20%", "bbox": [47.1, 880.1, 557.2, 902.7]}, {"text": "Senior Notes due 2016 and 5.40% Senior Notes due 2014.  The", "bbox": [47.1, 903.6, 570.2, 926.2]}, {"text": "tender offer for each series of notes expires on March 16, 2009.", "bbox": [47.1, 927.1, 571.2, 949.8]}, {"text": "Credit Ratings", "bbox": [47.1, 973.9, 176.4, 996.7]}, {"text": "Moody's, S&P and Fitch periodically review the credit ratings", "bbox": [47.1, 1021.0, 558.9, 1043.6]}, {"text": "on the debt and preferred securities of PPL and its subsidiaries.", "bbox": [47.1, 1044.5, 573.3, 1067.1]}, {"text": "Based on their respective independent reviews, the rating", "bbox": [47.1, 1068.0, 519.6, 1090.7]}, {"text": "agencies may make certain ratings revisions or ratings", "bbox": [47.1, 1091.4, 495.5, 1114.1]}, {"text": "affirmations.", "bbox": [47.1, 1115.0, 157.3, 1137.6]}, {"text": "A credit rating reflects an assessment by the rating agency of the", "bbox": [47.1, 1161.9, 580.5, 1184.6]}, {"text": "creditworthiness associated with an issuer and particular", "bbox": [47.1, 1185.4, 512.8, 1208.1]}, {"text": "securities that it issues.  The credit ratings of PPL and its", "bbox": [47.1, 1209.0, 516.7, 1231.6]}, {"text": "subsidiaries are based on information provided by PPL and", "bbox": [47.1, 1232.4, 535.9, 1255.0]}, {"text": "other sources.  The ratings of Moody's, S&P and Fitch are not a", "bbox": [47.1, 1255.9, 572.0, 1278.6]}, {"text": "recommendation to buy, sell or hold any securities of PPL or its", "bbox": [47.1, 1279.5, 574.1, 1302.1]}, {"text": "subsidiaries.  Such ratings may be subject to revisions or", "bbox": [47.1, 1302.9, 515.4, 1325.5]}, {"text": "withdrawal by the agencies at any time and should be evaluated", "bbox": [47.1, 1326.4, 573.1, 1349.1]}, {"text": "independently of each other and any other rating that may be", "bbox": [47.1, 1349.8, 549.1, 1372.5]}, {"text": "assigned to the securities.  A downgrade in PPL's or its", "bbox": [47.1, 1373.3, 501.3, 1396.0]}, {"text": "subsidiaries' credit ratings could result in higher borrowing costs", "bbox": [47.1, 1396.9, 579.9, 1419.5]}, {"text": "and reduced access to capital markets.", "bbox": [47.1, 1420.3, 364.3, 1442.9]}, {"text": "The following table summarizes the credit ratings of PPL and its", "bbox": [47.1, 1467.4, 580.2, 1490.0]}, {"text": "rated subsidiaries at December 31, 2008.", "bbox": [47.1, 1490.8, 385.6, 1513.4]}, {"text": "Moody's", "bbox": [900.3, 100.6, 964.3, 118.7]}, {"text": "S&P", "bbox": [1024.2, 100.6, 1060.9, 118.7]}, {"text": "Fitch (a)", "bbox": [1117.1, 100.2, 1175.6, 118.3]}, {"text": "PPL", "bbox": [650.0, 120.3, 680.8, 138.4]}, {"text": "Issuer Rating", "bbox": [672.9, 138.8, 763.7, 156.9]}, {"text": "Baa2", "bbox": [913.5, 138.8, 951.2, 156.9]}, {"text": "BBB", "bbox": [1024.3, 138.8, 1061.1, 156.9]}, {"text": "BBB", "bbox": [1129.9, 138.8, 1166.7, 156.9]}, {"text": "Outlook