, "bbox": [650.0, 1139.2, 669.1, 1157.3]}, {"text": "Excludes Exempt Facilities Revenue Bonds issued by the PEDFA on behalf", "bbox": [685.3, 1139.2, 1185.8, 1157.3]}, {"text": "of PPL Energy Supply, some of which are currently supported by a letter of", "bbox": [685.3, 1158.0, 1183.9, 1176.0]}, {"text": "credit and are rated on the basis of the credit enhancement.", "bbox": [685.3, 1176.8, 1073.8, 1194.9]}, {"text": "(c)", "bbox": [650.0, 1195.6, 668.1, 1213.6]}, {"text": "Excludes Pollution Control Revenue Bonds issued by the LCIDA and the", "bbox": [685.4, 1195.6, 1169.2, 1213.6]}, {"text": "PEDFA on behalf of PPL Electric, of which the LCIDA bonds are insured", "bbox": [685.3, 1214.3, 1174.5, 1232.4]}, {"text": "and may be rated on the basis of relevant factors, including the insurer's", "bbox": [685.3, 1233.2, 1158.2, 1251.3]}, {"text": "ratings.", "bbox": [685.3, 1252.0, 737.9, 1270.0]}, {"text": "Moody's and S&P did not take any actions related to PPL and its", "bbox": [650.0, 1294.5, 1184.4, 1317.1]}, {"text": "rated subsidiaries during 2008.  Fitch took the following actions", "bbox": [650.0, 1317.9, 1178.9, 1340.5]}, {"text": "in 2008:", "bbox": [650.0, 1341.4, 722.8, 1364.1]}, {"text": "x In March 2008, Fitch completed a review of its credit ratings", "bbox": [650.0, 1388.3, 1170.8, 1413.9]}, {"text": "for PPL, PPL Capital Funding, PPL Energy Supply and PPL", "bbox": [668.4, 1411.9, 1167.4, 1434.5]}, {"text": "Electric and affirmed all ratings related to these entities, with", "bbox": [668.4, 1435.4, 1173.0, 1458.0]}, {"text": "the exception that it lowered the preferred stock rating of PPL", "bbox": [668.4, 1458.8, 1179.5, 1481.5]}, {"text": "Electric to BBB from BBB+.  Fitch stated in the related press", "bbox": [668.4, 1482.3, 1175.5, 1505.0]}, {"text": "release that the lower preferred stock rating reflects its junior", "bbox": [668.4, 1505.9, 1172.2, 1528.5]}]}